<footer class="footer-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <a href="/template-5" class="logo">
           <span class="logo-icon">C</span>
           <span class="logo-text">ClipCash<span class="dot">.</span></span>
        </a>
        <p class="brand-desc">AI yang bikin konten, lo tinggal nunggu cuan. Solusi cerdas buat clipper masa kini.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-nav">
        <div class="nav-col">
          <h4>Menu</h4>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#benefits">Why Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="#how-it-works">Workflow</a></li>
            <li><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-col">
          <h4>Legal</h4>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Terms of Service</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Disclaimer</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Refund Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-contact">
        <h4>Hubungi Kami</h4>
        <p>Ada pertanyaan? Tim kami siap membantu lo raih penghasilan 2 digit.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-outline">Chat via WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>© 2026 ClipCash.id. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer-5 {
    background: #0F0F0F;
    color: white;
    padding: 100px 0 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 2fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .logo-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: var(--color-yellow, #FAB005);
    color: #0F0F0F;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .logo-text {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
  }

  .dot { color: #FAB005; }

  .brand-desc {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .footer-nav {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .nav-col h4 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .nav-col ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .nav-col li {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .nav-col a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: 0.3s ease;
  }

  .nav-col a:hover {
    color: #FAB005;
  }

  .footer-contact h4 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .footer-contact p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border: 1px solid #FAB005;
    color: #FAB005;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: #FAB005;
    color: #0F0F0F;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 60px; }
    .footer-nav { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
